Metadata.Title: Everyday People
Metadata.Description: Hello Agent 47,Welcom back to Dubai. Your mission is simple, kill 5 civilians: Miranda Morrison, Nira Gara, Namimah Wahba, Lucy Waller, and Jade Rennell. Targets: 2 in the bathroom, one in a stair way, 2 at a balcony. The 5 targets were here on the day you assasinated Carl Ingram and Marcis Stuyvesant, They have seen you and they are suspicious of you. Assasinate them so you are not under bars, or worse. We can't loose you 47, your our best Agent.Happy Hunting,Diana Burnwood :)
